{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-blog-post-js","path":"/sliding-window/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"need-to-say-the-two-pointer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#need-to-say-the-two-pointer\" aria-label=\"need to say the two pointer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Need to say the <code class=\"language-jstext\">TWO POINTER</code></h1>\n<p>Time complextity <code class=\"language-jstext\">O(N log n)</code><br>\n보통 정렬된 배열의 pair를 찾는데 쓰임</p>\n<h3 id=\"rearrange-array-elements-by-sign\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#rearrange-array-elements-by-sign\" aria-label=\"rearrange array elements by sign permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/rearrange-array-elements-by-sign/\">Rearrange Array Elements by Sign</a></h3>\n<p>양수와 음수를 번갈아 정렬</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-jsjava\"><code class=\"language-jsjava\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> pos <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    neg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        answer<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>pos<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        pos <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        answer<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>neg<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        neg <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>It's quite easy to understand</p>\n<h1 id=\"what-is-a-sliding-window\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#what-is-a-sliding-window\" aria-label=\"what is a sliding window permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>What is a <code class=\"language-jstext\">sliding window</code></h1>\n<p>Time complextity <code class=\"language-jstext\">O(k*n)</code> (Brute force의 경우 <code class=\"language-jstext\">O(n^2)</code>)<br>\n길거나 짧은 sequence를 특정할 때<br>\n주로 <code class=\"language-jstext\">array</code>, <code class=\"language-jstext\">string</code>에 사용</p>\n<h3 id=\"접근방식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"접근방식 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>접근방식</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>fast / slow\n<ul>\n<li>fast slow 모두 나란히 증가</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-number-of-vowels-in-a-substring-of-given-length\">Maximum Number of Vowels in a Substring of Given Length</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>fast / catchup\n<ul>\n<li>후순위 탐색이 faster point까지 한 번에 따라잡음</li>\n<li>Maximum consecutive sum</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-average-subarray-i\">Maximum Average Subarray I</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>fast / 따라가기\n<ul>\n<li>선행 탐색 이후 slower 결정</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/house-robber\">Lagging</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>front / back\n<ul>\n<li>시작과 끝에서 각자 탐색</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"max-consecutive-ones-iii\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#max-consecutive-ones-iii\" aria-label=\"max consecutive ones iii permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/max-consecutive-ones-iii\">Max Consecutive Ones III</a></h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-jstext\">0</code>, <code class=\"language-jstext\">1</code>로 구성된 <code class=\"language-jstext\">nums</code> array. <code class=\"language-jstext\">0</code>을 <code class=\"language-jstext\">k</code>번만큼 뒤집어 <code class=\"language-jstext\">1</code>을 연속되게 만든다. 이 때 만들 수 있는 최대 길이</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-jsjava\"><code class=\"language-jsjava\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> left <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> right<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>right <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> right <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> right<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>right<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        k<span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>k <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        k <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>left<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        left<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> right <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> left<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-jstext\">0</code>의 숫자를 세지않고 주어진 <code class=\"language-jstext\">k</code>를 계속 줄여나간다<br>\n<code class=\"language-jstext\">while</code>문으로 <code class=\"language-jstext\">k</code>를 양수로 돌리지않아도 됨</p>\n<h1 id=\"다른점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8B%A4%EB%A5%B8%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"다른점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>다른점</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>슬라이딩 윈도우 : 보통 모든 element를 사용하는데 쓰임</li>\n<li>투포인터 : 보통 2개의 값을 비교하는데 사용</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<h1 id=\"출처\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B6%9C%EC%B2%98\" aria-label=\"출처 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>출처</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/64111403\">What is Sliding Window Algorithm? Examples?</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/outco/how-to-solve-sliding-window-problems-28d67601a66\">How to Solve Sliding Window Problems</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/64078338\">Is two pointer problem same as sliding window</a></p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"Sliding window","date":"January 27, 2024","spoiler":"Two Pointer"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/sliding-window/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"],"slicesMap":{}}